name: IN DEPTH WITH SAKURA ANDO (III)
description:
0,5 MIRI
.
Sawa Yamagishi worked as a nursing-care helper.
The family of an old man asked Sawa to sleep with him
which led her to eventually lose her job and house.
Now, she has nowhere to go.
Sawa finds elderly people in trouble and gets involved in their lives.
Meeting them, their lives change and Sawa's own wounds start to heal.
.
I love her in every film performance, she can glued the watchers into depth feelings.
